<br>
I think it's bullshit the republicans are digging up any archaic law to stifle the public.  They own the media and can control them but unfortunately they can't control every individual citizen (yet, new laws and legislation withstanding). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=linale>Linale</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 290<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(6/27/03 1:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=115.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Freedom of Speech</span><hr size=1> It was one person.  He apparently has been arrested in the past, and for illegal activities.  I don't recall protestors being arrested unless they were doing stupid shit like blocking traffic and interferring with others in public.<br>
<br>
No brownie points on this case.  Move on. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kerai>Kerai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Teh Anti-American</span><br>  Posts: 4744<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(6/27/03 1:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=115.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.sowned.com/bleh/kerai2.gif height=77 width=69></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Freedom of Speech</span><hr size=1> Walking inside an airport is clearly blocking traffic. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=477296">Kerai</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
